title: Douyara Watashi no Karada wa Kanzen Muteki no you desu ne
original_name: どうやら私の身体は完全無敵のようですね
sinopse:
A girl who regrets dying without being filial to her parents wishes that in her next life that she will have a body that is invincible. God decides to grant her that wish, and she awakes suddenly in the body of a baby... Could this be reincarnation?

(Source: MU)
